rows.label: tev040401_SEL0011
rows.name: Ask Oll about Oblivia.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev040401_JNK0020
rows.name: Discuss[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev040401_SEL0021
rows.name: Ask Oll about recent developments.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev040401_SEL0031
rows.name: Ask Oll about tyrants in Oblivia.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev040401_SEL0041
rows.name: Ask Oll about tyrants in Oblivia.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev040401_MSG0001
rows.name: Do you know silvery cactaceous resin?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev040401_MSG0002
rows.name: It is precious. Even Ganglion scour Oblivia to find it.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev040401_MSG0003
rows.name:
But I know secret. Resin only found near River Isle
on morning of days when rains fall.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev040401_MSG0004
rows.name:
Cavern Clan tortured me for secret. But I did not tell.
Now only you know![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev040401_MSG0005
rows.name:
Did you like secret? Then come visit again.
I will tell you all I remember.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev040401_MSG0008
rows.name: I feel better. Earth aliens feed Prone well.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev040401_MSG0009
rows.name:
Thank you for saving us. Rada and I will hunt.
Get strong. Then help you annihilate Cavern Clan
and Ganglion![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev040401_MSG0010
rows.name:
Prone always return kindness with kindness.
And violence with violence.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev040401_MSG0015
rows.name: In Oblivia, I saw monster with no head![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev040401_MSG0016
rows.name: Ganglion call this beast "millesaur."[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev040401_MSG0017
rows.name:
Millesaur hobbled around weakly.
Probably seeking brave warrior to give it final rest.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev040401_MSG0018
rows.name:
...Where is millesaur? Near North Coast base camp.
But you should not fight it. You should stay away.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev040401_MSG0023
rows.name: I heard rumor of strong foe.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev040401_MSG0024
rows.name: Tyrant called Hartmut, the Calamity plagues Oblivia.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev040401_MSG0025
rows.name:
Prone friend says Hartmut circles the Yawning Giant
without fear.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev040401_MSG0026
rows.name:
Some say that creature's maw can rend ground.
I must look like nothing more than guineyrat to it![ST:wait ]
